l%5D2021-01-14&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=2d7573f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/channel/364/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B]即時中國[/url]撰文：[url=]蘇子牧[/url]2021-01-14</a> 13:31最後更新日期：2021-01-14 13:31連日來，新冠肺炎疫情在多個省市反彈，其中河北省疫情最為嚴重。據新華社消息，河北石家莊目前正在建設集中隔離點。中鐵十四局集團滹沱河生態修復三期工程項目部於13日接到通知，參建石家莊市集中隔離點，施工場地位於正定縣文正大街諸福屯鎮固營村，佔地約500畝。現場畫面顯示，30餘台剷車和推土機於13日晚已開始進行場地的地表清理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/4c60fb79a84090c688f7ebf8313c7c63.jpg/FiqI3A6OVkwX5vSpkilCbChnN62HdFbeHYYslh2GLJY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F4c60fb79a84090c688f7ebf8313c7c63.jpg%2FFiqI3A6OVkwX5vSpkilCbChnN62HdFbeHYYslh2GLJY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3d840706&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/b632e88c180e2c2474c5d92d84578764.jpg/fygf3ylTRqLz7oSTjp8RsIqrGKb2BPK8pc8-4aXPPuE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2Fb632e88c180e2c2474c5d92d84578764.jpg%2Ffygf3ylTRqLz7oSTjp8RsIqrGKb2BPK8pc8-4aXPPuE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=199dbb9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/c43639f77cf162b717cc145d9c11953d.jpg/zUOeAwLJMpGCZ3mKbJUKK8WOok9tY9dvuyU1VrslNVY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2Fc43639f77cf162b717cc145d9c11953d.jpg%2FzUOeAwLJMpGCZ3mKbJUKK8WOok9tY9dvuyU1VrslNVY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ee6eb873&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/2f51f9154d9057be7a030b84158c4a8d.jpg/PA7dd0NjeSNIIc6ta9Xj8wju1Q2WE_LjT9Wdkk_VnZI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F2f51f9154d9057be7a030b84158c4a8d.jpg%2FPA7dd0NjeSNIIc6ta9Xj8wju1Q2WE_LjT9Wdkk_VnZI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=49859a71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/7b19244aa0fba98fdba13184a4011fd5.jpg/fNYOxcfm4LFWyDz0hXIeTvGtAtd82knMh8-G6IfPhug?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F7b19244aa0fba98fdba13184a4011fd5.jpg%2FfNYOxcfm4LFWyDz0hXIeTvGtAtd82knMh8-G6IfPhug%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=eee8c599&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/f7ec6af8e6635892a75c9e4bca684416.jpg/RekMIQlLAFoxB3DK7f7gP4GbjDX9nRhUwsPORMLDzkQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2Ff7ec6af8e6635892a75c9e4bca684416.jpg%2FRekMIQlLAFoxB3DK7f7gP4GbjDX9nRhUwsPORMLDzkQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3bb1b9b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/a62573d0e417821dfaacd487ca484caf.jpg/7oSZbikEZUmWLVA7cWXxNo_SzHW8mipZG5SD_RuUg_0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2Fa62573d0e417821dfaacd487ca484caf.jpg%2F7oSZbikEZUmWLVA7cWXxNo_SzHW8mipZG5SD_RuUg_0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f42ab017&s={SIZE}\" />項目經理部副經理馬少海介紹，項目部13日11時接到上級通知，參建石家莊市集中隔離點的基建施工。目前已有100餘人、數十台運輸車輛、平地機、剷車等工程設備進場。<br />\n基建部分完工後，3,000套集成房屋將在硬化的場地上迅速拼裝到位。這些集成房屋正由唐山市陸續運抵正定縣，預計3天內可接連抵達。<br />\n目前，唐山市蘆台經濟開發區的三家集成房屋生產企業正在加班加點生產。據悉，這三家集成房屋生產企業都曾在2020年初為武漢火神山等醫療機構提供過集成房屋。此次支援石家莊的集成房屋每套面積為18平方米，採用輕鋼結構，具有運輸便捷、安裝迅速、可回收利用等優點。"},{"pid":"1447091a931b5334275425a833f5a1cbe381c4e3","tid":2369890,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"上次條數找左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee864aa3cbd2817fdf24cb33630460175813227","tid":2369890,"uid":87515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.winudf.com/v2/image1/Y29tLkd1aWRlLkNSQUZUUElBR0FNRV9zY3JlZW5fMV8xNjAxMTMwNDAxXzAyNw/screen-1.jpg?fakeurl=1&amp;type=.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.winudf.com%2Fv2%2Fimage1%2FY29tLkd1aWRlLkNSQUZUUElBR0FNRV9zY3JlZW5fMV8xNjAxMTMwNDAxXzAyNw%2Fscreen-1.jpg%3